headline: Coterra Energy Schedules Second-Quarter 2025 Results Conference Call for Tuesday, August 5, 2025
summary: HOUSTON, July 08, 2025--Coterra Energy Inc. ("Coterra" or the "Company") (NYSE: CTRA) today announced it will host a conference call on Tuesday, August 5, 2025, at 9:00 AM CT (10:00 AM ET) to discuss second-quarter 2025 financial and operating results. The Company plans to announce second-quarter 2025 results after the market closes on Monday, August 4, 2025.
